	<ThingDef ParentName="GW_Rulers_ShoulderBase">
		<defName>GW_Rulers_ValdorShoulderW</defName>
		<label>Corinthine Warplate shoulders (W)</label>
		<description>The auramite shoulder pauldrons of the Corinthine Warplate, gleaming in its splendor. \n\nConstantin Valdor fought valiantly in defense of Terra, boarding the &lt;i&gt;Vengeful Spirit&lt;/i&gt; but becoming separated from the Emperor in a trap. Assailed by First Captain Ezekyle Abaddon of the Sons of Horus, he duelled the Traitor Marine and managed to cut him with the Apollonian Spear. However, as the Spear gave him an insight into the next ten thousand years of war and destruction, the horrified Captain-General named Abaddon "the Despoiler" - a title that the latter has used ever since.</description>
